These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, chaman, tiparillo
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, software-developer
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, monopoly
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, western, sports
 1. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the accountant is the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the person watching action movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching sports movies##2
10. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
11. the accountant is the owner of the rat##1
12. the software-developer is the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Cigar          | siglo   | tiparillo            | chaman     |
| Job           | accountant | software-developer | dressmaker |
| Game   | chess      | monopoly               | backgammon        |
| Pet           | rat        | chinchilla         | goldfish   |
| Sport         | tennis     | skateboarding      | golf       |
| Movie-Genre     | sports        | western              | action       |

