.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: german, japanese, pakistani
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, documentary
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, cape-cod
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, snake
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer, librarian
 1. the german is the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the librarian##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 4. the pakistani is the futuristic house##1
 5. the librarian is between the german and the person watching crime movies##2
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the japanese and the software-developer##2
 7. the person drinking milk is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the german is on the right of the pakistani##1
 9. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
10. the cape-cod house is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | lemonade | milk        |
| Nationality          | japanese   | pakistani    | german        |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | disaster | documentary |
| House   | cape-cod   | futuristic  | gothic-revival         |
| Pet           | snake    | hedgehog | mouse       |
| Job     | freelancer   | librarian    | software-developer  |

