.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, pink, blue
City: venice, boston, miami
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, indonesian, japanese
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, entrepreneur, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, western
3 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rat
 1. the chef is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
 2. the scientist is the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes pink##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person traveling to venice is between the indonesian and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 7. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 9. the scientist is on the far right##1
10. the japanese is in an odd position##4
11. the indonesian is the entrepreneur##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
13. the brazilian is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Color      | pink        | fuchsia     | blue          |
| City          | boston     | venice | miami    |
| Nationality         | indonesian    | brazilian  | japanese |
| Job           | entrepreneur | chef    | scientist    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery      | western | fantasy      |
| Pet           | cat          | rat     | pony         |

