.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, scooter, motorbike
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading
House: victorian, craftsman, modern
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, soul
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, sailing
 1. the craftsman house is on the right of the modern house##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of d&b is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 6. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 8. the victorian house is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
11. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Transport      | scooter  | motorbike      | ship        |
| Hobby         | reading   | cooking     | magic-tricks |
| House   | victorian | modern | craftsman     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | d&b         | soul         |
| Pet   | rabbit   | goat     | dog      |
| Sport         | baseball  | sailing     | golf         |

