 2. the american is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating cherry##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the thai is on the left of the freelancer##1
 6. the police-officer is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the american##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
12. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
