There are 3 different nationalities: british, german, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skiing, tennis
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the person eating pomegranate and the nigerian##2
3. the british is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating strawberry##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who growspoppy and the person drinking juice##2
9. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice    | iced-tea           | 7up         |
| Food         | strawberry   | tomato             | pomegranate  |
| Flower           | amaryllis  | iris | poppy |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | mystery              | epic      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | german             | british     |
| Sport         | skiing   | handball           | tennis      |

