.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, sunflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, punk, techno
City: liverpool, marseilles, rome
3 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, snake
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, tiparillo
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 3. the person driving the car is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 5. the person driving the car is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of country##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the fan of country##1
 9. the fan of punk is the person who growsazalea##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| Flower          | azalea    | sunflower  | balloon-flower   |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | country  | techno  |
| City   | liverpool | marseilles  | rome |
| Pet           | mouse     | lizard   | snake   |
| Cigar         | blend  | alhambra | tiparillo |
| Transport     | scooter   | car      | roller  |

