.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, horse
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, mechanic, photographer
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, bike
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, siglo
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the person driving the bike is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the photographer is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the librarian is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the mechanic##1
10. the mechanic is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Pet          | goat     | horse   | hedgehog     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | collecting   | gardening  |
| Job           | librarian   | photographer | mechanic   |
| Transport   | ship    | helicopter       | bike    |
| Cigar   | siglo        | blend    | pall-mall   |
| Sport         | rowing      | biathlon     | water-polo |

 